{"type":"click","text":"D\n    \n      Hybrid: Serpent Wrapped Around Core\n      Combine A and B. A sleek digital serpent coiled around a glowing core/sphere. On scroll, the serpent uncoils and the core explodes simultaneously — the serpent's body fractures to reveal internal circuitry while the core disperses into constellation-like data nodes. Two brand symbols fusing into one moment.\n      \n        ProsMaximum brand impact — serpent + AI core = OphidianAIMore complex animation = more impressive scroll-scrubThe uncoiling motion adds a dynamic element beyond just \"explosion\"\n        ConsMost complex to generate — multiple subjects in frameRisk of visual clutter if not carefully composedNano Banana 2 may struggle with this level of specificity","choice":"d","id":null,"timestamp":1773526523232}
